do not install. Prefer a version of the skill that explicitly lists required binaries and environment variables (e.g., SLACK_BOT_TOKEN) and provides a trusted source/homepage for the tool.",model:"gpt-5-mini",status:"suspicious",summary:"The skill's described functionality is coherent with controlling Slack, but the SKILL.md expects a 'slack' CLI and a bot token while the registry metadata does not declare any required binary or credential — an important mismatch you should resolve before installing.",verdict:"suspicious"},parsed:$R[26]={},sha256hash:"3fb592fd566fd42495c863b285303d4092debb58c912e91498f4e523dd4b60dc",skillId:"kd7aqq9ye7nqa4wwecyvshc5bx7yjz2s",version:"1.0.0",vtAnalysis:$R[27]={analysis:"Type: OpenClaw Skill\nName: slack\nVersion: 1.0.0\n\nThe OpenClaw skill bundle for Slack is benign. The `SKILL.md` defines a set of actions (react, send/edit/delete messages, manage pins, fetch member info) that are standard for a Slack integration. It explicitly states it uses a pre-configured bot token and does not contain any instructions for data exfiltration, malicious execution, persistence, or prompt injection against the agent beyond its stated purpose of interacting with Slack.",checkedAt:1774407622203,source:"palm",status:"clean",verdict:"benign"}},moderationInfo:null,owner:$R[28]={_creationTime:1767472433734.8093,_id:"publishers:steipete",displayName:"Peter Steinberger",handle:"steipete",image:"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/58493?v=4",kind:"user",linkedUserId:"kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26"},pendingReview:!1,requestedSlug:"slack",resolvedSlug:"slack",skill:$R[29]={_creationTime:1767545378001.9133,_id:"kd7aqq9ye7nqa4wwecyvshc5bx7yjz2s",badges:$R[30]={highlighted:$R[31]={at:1769571860347,byUserId:"kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26"}},createdAt:1767545378002,displayName:"Slack",latestVersionId:"k974s2nwqdrhhcyyetbj0d3x8h7ykacv",ownerUserId:"kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26",slug:"slack",stats:$R[32]={comments:11,downloads:32533,installsAllTime:1193,installsCurrent:1168,stars:108,versions:1},summary:"Use when you need to control Slack from Clawdbot via the slack tool, including reacting to messages or pinning/unpinning items in Slack channels or DMs.",tags:$R[33]={latest:"k974s2nwqdrhhcyyetbj0d3x8h7ykacv"},updatedAt:1772064940106}},readme:"---\nname: slack\ndescription: Use when you need to control Slack from Clawdbot via the slack tool, including reacting to messages or pinning/unpinning items in Slack channels or DMs.\n---\n\n# Slack Actions\n\n## Overview\n\nUse `slack` to react, manage pins, send/edit/delete messages, and fetch member info. The tool uses the bot token configured for Clawdbot.\n\n## Inputs to collect\n\n- `channelId` and `messageId` (Slack message timestamp, e.g. `1712023032.1234`).\n- For reactions, an `emoji` (Unicode or `:name:`).\n- For message sends, a `to` target (`channel:\x3Cid>` or `user:\x3Cid>`) and `content`.\n\nMessage context lines include `slack message id` and `channel` fields you can reuse directly.\n\n## Actions\n\n### Action groups\n\n| Action group | Default | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| reactions | enabled | React + list reactions |\n| messages | enabled | Read/send/edit/delete |\n| pins | enabled | Pin/unpin/list |\n| memberInfo | enabled | Member info |\n| emojiList | enabled | Custom emoji list |\n\n### React to a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"react\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\",\n  \"emoji\": \"✅\"\n}\n```\n\n### List reactions\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"reactions\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\"\n}\n```\n\n### Send a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"sendMessage\",\n  \"to\": \"channel:C123\",\n  \"content\": \"Hello from Clawdbot\"\n}\n```\n\n### Edit a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"editMessage\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\",\n  \"content\": \"Updated text\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"deleteMessage\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\"\n}\n```\n\n### Read recent messages\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"readMessages\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"limit\": 20\n}\n```\n\n### Pin a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"pinMessage\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\"\n}\n```\n\n### Unpin a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"unpinMessage\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\"\n}\n```\n\n### List pinned items\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"listPins\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\"\n}\n```\n\n### Member info\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"memberInfo\",\n  \"userId\": \"U123\"\n}\n```\n\n### Emoji list\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"emojiList\"\n}\n```\n\n## Ideas to try\n\n- React with ✅ to mark completed tasks.\n- Pin key decisions or weekly status updates.\n",readmeError:null}},ssr:!0}],lastMatchId:"␀$owner␀$slug␀steipete␀slack"})($R["tsr"]);$_TSR.e();document.currentScript.remove()</script><script type="module" async="">import("/assets/main-C_iS0jIE.js")</script></body></html>